[FILE:307:descriptions/desc.single]
Geoclue is a D-Bus service that provides location information. The primary 
goal of the Geoclue project is to make creating location-aware 
applications as simple as possible, while the secondary goal is to ensure 
that no application can access location information without explicit 
permission from user.


